Revision history for mocha

0.002   24/02/2013
        - New Feature: Override the default OOP framework using 'with'
          - use mocha with => 'Moose';
        - Changed: To turn off a feature, add it inside an arrayref with 'no'
          - use mocha no => [qw/ sigs oop /];
        - Changed: Turn mocha into a role with 'as'
          - use mocha as => 'role';

0.001   23/02/2013
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.

